"bhāsamānānaṃ saddaṃ suṇātha:"
msgstr ""
"‘But have you ever heard the voice of the deities reborn in an exclusively "
"happy world saying:"

msgctxt "dn9:53.3"
msgid ""
"“suppaṭipannāttha, mārisā, ujuppaṭipannāttha, mārisā, ekantasukhassa lokassa "
"sacchikiriyāya;"
msgstr ""
"“Practice well, dear sirs, practice directly so as to realize an exclusively "
"happy world."

msgctxt "dn9:53.4"
msgid "mayampi hi, mārisā, evaṃpaṭipannā ekantasukhaṃ lokaṃ upapannā”’ti?"
msgstr ""
