"Saṅkilesikā ceva dhammā pahīyissanti, vodāniyā ca dhammā abhivaḍḍhissanti, "
"paññāpāripūriṃ vepullattañca diṭṭheva dhamme sayaṃ abhiññā sacchikatvā "
"upasampajja viharissati, pāmujjañceva bhavissati pīti ca passaddhi ca sati "
"ca sampajaññañca sukho ca vihāro."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="64"></a><a class="wp" id="wp42"></a><a class="pts"
#. id="pts1.197"></a>
msgctxt "dn9:73.1"
msgid ""
"Arūpassapi kho ahaṃ, poṭṭhapāda, attapaṭilābhassa pahānāya dhammaṃ desemi:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn9:73.2"
msgid ""
"‘yathāpaṭipannānaṃ vo saṅkilesikā dhammā pahīyissanti, vodāniyā dhammā "
"abhivaḍḍhissanti, paññāpāripūriṃ vepullattañca diṭṭheva dhamme sayaṃ abhiññā "
"sacchikatvā upasampajja viharissathā’ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn9:73.3"
msgid "Siyā kho pana te, poṭṭhapāda, evamassa:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn9:73.4"
msgid ""
"‘saṅkilesikā dhammā pahīyissanti, vodāniyā dhammā abhivaḍḍhissanti, "
"paññāpāripūriṃ vepullattañca diṭṭheva dhamme sayaṃ abhiññā sacchikatvā "
"upasampajja viharissati, dukkho ca kho vihāro’ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn9:73.5"
msgid "Na kho panetaṃ, poṭṭhapāda, evaṃ daṭṭhabbaṃ."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn9:73.6"
msgid ""
"Saṅkilesikā ceva dhammā pahīyissanti, vodāniyā ca dhammā abhivaḍḍhissanti, "
"paññāpāripūriṃ vepullattañca diṭṭheva dhamme sayaṃ abhiññā sacchikatvā "
"upasampajja viharissati, pāmujjañceva bhavissati pīti ca passaddhi ca sati "
"ca sampajaññañca sukho ca vihāro."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="65"></a><a class="wp" id="wp43"></a>
msgctxt "dn9:74.1"
msgid "Pare ce, poṭṭhapāda, amhe evaṃ puccheyyuṃ:"
msgstr "If others should ask us,"

msgctxt "dn9:74.2"
msgid ""
"‘katamo pana so, āvuso, oḷāriko attapaṭilābho, yassa tumhe pahānāya dhammaṃ "
"desetha, yathāpaṭipannānaṃ vo saṅkilesikā dhammā pahīyissanti, vodāniyā "
"dhammā abhivaḍḍhissanti, paññāpāripūriṃ vepullattañca diṭṭheva dhamme sayaṃ "
"abhiññā sacchikatvā upasampajja viharissathā’ti, tesaṃ mayaṃ evaṃ puṭṭhā "
"evaṃ byākareyyāma:"
msgstr ""
"‘But Reverends, what is that substantial reincarnation?’ we’d answer like "
"this:"

msgctxt "dn9:74.3"
msgid ""
"‘ayaṃ vā so, āvuso, oḷāriko attapaṭilābho, yassa mayaṃ pahānāya dhammaṃ "
"desema, yathāpaṭipannānaṃ vo saṅkilesikā dhammā pahīyissanti, vodāniyā "
"dhammā abhivaḍḍhissanti, paññāpāripūriṃ vepullattañca diṭṭheva dhamme sayaṃ "
"abhiññā sacchikatvā upasampajja viharissathā’ti."
msgstr "‘This is that substantial reincarnation.’"

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="66"></a><a class="wp" id="wp44"></a><a class="pts"
#. id="pts1.198"></a>
msgctxt "dn9:75.1"
msgid "Pare ce, poṭṭhapāda, amhe evaṃ puccheyyuṃ:"
msgstr "If others should ask us,"

msgctxt "dn9:75.2"
msgid ""
"‘katamo pana so, āvuso, manomayo attapaṭilābho, yassa tumhe pahānāya dhammaṃ "
"desetha, yathāpaṭipannānaṃ vo saṅkilesikā dhammā pahīyissanti, vodāniyā "
"dhammā abhivaḍḍhissanti, paññāpāripūriṃ vepullattañca diṭṭheva dhamme sayaṃ "
"abhiññā sacchikatvā upasampajja viharissathā’ti?"
msgstr ""
"‘But Reverends, what is that mind-made reincarnation?’ we’d answer like this:"

msgctxt "dn9:75.3"
msgid "Tesaṃ mayaṃ evaṃ puṭṭhā evaṃ byākareyyāma:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn9:75.4"
msgid ""
"‘ayaṃ vā so, āvuso, manomayo attapaṭilābho yassa mayaṃ pahānāya dhammaṃ "
"desema, yathāpaṭipannānaṃ vo saṅkilesikā dhammā pahīyissanti, vodāniyā "
"dhammā abhivaḍḍhissanti, paññāpāripūriṃ vepullattañca diṭṭheva dhamme sayaṃ "
"abhiññā sacchikatvā upasampajja viharissathā’ti."
msgstr "‘This is that mind-made reincarnation.’"

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="67"></a><a class="wp" id="wp45"></a>
msgctxt "dn9:76.1"
msgid "Pare ce, poṭṭhapāda, amhe evaṃ puccheyyuṃ:"
msgstr "If others should ask us,"

msgctxt "dn9:76.2"
msgid ""
"‘katamo pana so, āvuso, arūpo attapaṭilābho, yassa tumhe pahānāya dhammaṃ "
"desetha, yathāpaṭipannānaṃ vo saṅkilesikā dhammā pahīyissanti, vodāniyā "
"dhammā abhivaḍḍhissanti, paññāpāripūriṃ vepullattañca diṭṭheva dhamme sayaṃ "
"abhiññā sacchikatvā upasampajja viharissathā’ti?"
msgstr ""
"‘But Reverends, what is that non-physical reincarnation?’ we’d answer like "
"this:"

msgctxt "dn9:76.3"
msgid "Tesaṃ mayaṃ evaṃ puṭṭhā evaṃ byākareyyāma:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn9:76.4"
msgid ""
"‘ayaṃ vā so, āvuso, arūpo attapaṭilābho yassa mayaṃ pahānāya dhammaṃ desema, "
"yathāpaṭipannānaṃ vo saṅkilesikā dhammā pahīyissanti, vodāniyā dhammā "
"abhivaḍḍhissanti, paññāpāripūriṃ vepullattañca diṭṭheva dhamme sayaṃ abhiññā "
"sacchikatvā upasampajja viharissathā’ti."
msgstr "‘This is that non-physical reincarnation.’"

# This whole argument is odd, and I suspect it is corrupt.
#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="68"></a>
msgctxt "dn9:77.1"
msgid ""
"Taṃ kiṃ maññasi, poṭṭhapāda, nanu evaṃ sante sappāṭihīrakataṃ bhāsitaṃ "
"sampajjatī”ti?"
msgstr ""
"What do you think, Poṭṭhapāda? This being so, doesn’t that statement turn "
"out to have a demonstrable basis?”"

msgctxt "dn9:77.2"
msgid "“Addhā kho, bhante, evaṃ sante sappāṭihīrakataṃ bhāsitaṃ sampajjatī”ti."
msgstr "“Clearly that’s the case, sir.”"

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="69"></a><a class="wp" id="wp46"></a>
msgctxt "dn9:78.1"
msgid ""
"“Seyyathāpi, poṭṭhapāda, puriso nisseṇiṃ kareyya pāsādassa ārohaṇāya tasseva "
"pāsādassa heṭṭhā."
msgstr ""
"“Suppose a man was to build a ladder for climbing up to a stilt longhouse "
"right underneath that longhouse."

msgctxt "dn9:78.2"
msgid "Tamenaṃ evaṃ vadeyyuṃ:"
msgstr "They’d say to him:"

msgctxt "dn9:78.3"
msgid ""
"‘ambho purisa, yassa tvaṃ pāsādassa ārohaṇāya nisseṇiṃ karosi, jānāsi taṃ "
"pāsādaṃ, puratthimāya vā disāya dakkhiṇāya vā disāya pacchimāya vā disāya "
"uttarāya vā disāya ucco vā nīco vā majjhimo vā’ti?"
msgstr ""
"‘Mister, that stilt longhouse that you’re building a ladder for—do you know "
"whether it’s to the north, south, east or west? Or whether it’s tall or "
"short or medium?’"

msgctxt "dn9:78.4"
msgid "So evaṃ vadeyya:"
msgstr "He’d say: "

msgctxt "dn9:78.5"
msgid ""
"‘ayaṃ vā so, āvuso, pāsādo, yassāhaṃ ārohaṇāya nisseṇiṃ karomi, tasseva "
"pāsādassa heṭṭhā’ti."
msgstr ""
"‘This is that stilt longhouse for which I’m building a ladder, right "
"underneath it.’"

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="70"></a>
msgctxt "dn9:79.1"
msgid ""
"Taṃ kiṃ maññasi, poṭṭhapāda, nanu evaṃ sante tassa purisassa "
"sappāṭihīrakataṃ bhāsitaṃ sampajjatī”ti?"
msgstr ""
"What do you think, Poṭṭhapāda? This being so, doesn’t that man’s statement "
"turn out to have a demonstrable basis?”"

msgctxt "dn9:79.2"
msgid ""
"“Addhā kho, bhante, evaṃ sante tassa purisassa sappāṭihīrakataṃ bhāsitaṃ "
"sampajjatī”ti."
msgstr "“Clearly that’s the case, sir.”"

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="71"></a><a class="wp" id="wp47"></a><a class="pts"
#. id="pts1.199"></a>
msgctxt "dn9:80.1"
msgid "“Evameva kho, poṭṭhapāda, pare ce amhe evaṃ puccheyyuṃ:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn9:80.2"
msgid "‘katamo pana so, āvuso, oḷāriko attapaṭilābho …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn9:80.3"
msgid "pe …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn9:80.4"
msgid "katamo pana so, āvuso, manomayo attapaṭilābho …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn9:80.5"
msgid "pe …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn9:80.6"
msgid ""
"katamo pana so, āvuso, arūpo attapaṭilābho, yassa tumhe pahānāya dhammaṃ "
"desetha, yathāpaṭipannānaṃ vo saṅkilesikā dhammā pahīyissanti, vodāniyā "
"dhammā abhivaḍḍhissanti, paññāpāripūriṃ vepullattañca diṭṭheva dhamme sayaṃ "
"abhiññā sacchikatvā upasampajja viharissathā’ti?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn9:80.7"
msgid "Tesaṃ mayaṃ evaṃ puṭṭhā evaṃ byākareyyāma:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn9:80.8"
msgid ""
"‘ayaṃ vā so, āvuso, arūpo attapaṭilābho, yassa mayaṃ pahānāya dhammaṃ "
"desema, yathāpaṭipannānaṃ vo saṅkilesikā dhammā pahīyissanti, vodāniyā "
"dhammā abhivaḍḍhissanti, paññāpāripūriṃ vepullattañca diṭṭheva dhamme sayaṃ "
"abhiññā sacchikatvā upasampajja viharissathā’ti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="72"></a>
msgctxt "dn9:81.1"
msgid ""
"Taṃ kiṃ maññasi, poṭṭhapāda, nanu evaṃ sante sappāṭihīrakataṃ bhāsitaṃ "
"sampajjatī”ti?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn9:81.2"
msgid "“Addhā kho, bhante, evaṃ sante sappāṭihīrakataṃ bhāsitaṃ sampajjatī”ti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="73"></a><a class="wp" id="wp48"></a>
msgctxt "dn9:82.1"
msgid "Evaṃ vutte, citto hatthisāriputto bhagavantaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr "When the Buddha had spoken, Citta Hatthisāriputta said:"

msgctxt "dn9:82.2"
msgid ""
"“yasmiṃ, bhante, samaye oḷāriko attapaṭilābho hoti, moghassa tasmiṃ samaye "
"manomayo attapaṭilābho hoti, mogho arūpo attapaṭilābho hoti;"
msgstr ""
"“Sir, while in a substantial reincarnation, are the mind-made and non-"
"physical reincarnations fictitious,"

msgctxt "dn9:82.3"
msgid "oḷāriko vāssa attapaṭilābho tasmiṃ samaye sacco hoti."
msgstr "and only the substantial reincarnation real?"

msgctxt "dn9:82.4"
msgid ""
"Yasmiṃ, bhante, samaye manomayo attapaṭilābho hoti, moghassa tasmiṃ samaye "
"oḷāriko attapaṭilābho hoti, mogho arūpo attapaṭilābho hoti;"
msgstr ""
"While in a mind-made reincarnation, are the substantial and non-physical "
"reincarnations fictitious,"

msgctxt "dn9:82.5"
msgid "manomayo vāssa attapaṭilābho tasmiṃ samaye sacco hoti."
msgstr "and only the mind-made reincarnation real?"

msgctxt "dn9:82.6"
msgid ""
"Yasmiṃ, bhante, samaye arūpo attapaṭilābho hoti, moghassa tasmiṃ samaye "
"oḷāriko attapaṭilābho hoti, mogho manomayo attapaṭilābho hoti;"
msgstr ""
"While in a non-physical reincarnation, are the substantial and mind-made "
"reincarnations fictitious,"

msgctxt "dn9:82.7"
msgid "arūpo vāssa attapaṭilābho tasmiṃ samaye sacco hotī”ti."
msgstr "and only the non-physical reincarnation real?”"

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="74"></a><a class="wp" id="wp49"></a><a class="pts"
#. id="pts1.200"></a>
msgctxt "dn9:83.1"
msgid ""
"“Yasmiṃ, citta, samaye oḷāriko attapaṭilābho hoti, neva tasmiṃ samaye "
"manomayo attapaṭilābhoti saṅkhaṃ gacchati, na arūpo attapaṭilābhoti saṅkhaṃ "
"gacchati;"
msgstr ""
"“While in a substantial reincarnation, it’s not referred to as a mind-made "
"or non-physical reincarnation,"

msgctxt "dn9:83.2"
msgid "oḷāriko attapaṭilābhotveva tasmiṃ samaye saṅkhaṃ gacchati."
msgstr "only as a substantial reincarnation."

msgctxt "dn9:83.3"
msgid ""
"Yasmiṃ, citta, samaye manomayo attapaṭilābho hoti, neva tasmiṃ samaye "
"oḷāriko attapaṭilābhoti saṅkhaṃ gacchati, na arūpo attapaṭilābhoti saṅkhaṃ "
"gacchati;"
msgstr ""
"While in a mind-made reincarnation, it’s not referred to as a substantial or "
"non-physical reincarnation,"

msgctxt "dn9:83.4"
msgid "manomayo attapaṭilābhotveva tasmiṃ samaye saṅkhaṃ gacchati."
msgstr "only as a mind-made reincarnation."

msgctxt "dn9:83.5"
msgid ""
"Yasmiṃ, citta, samaye arūpo attapaṭilābho hoti, neva tasmiṃ samaye oḷāriko "
"attapaṭilābhoti saṅkhaṃ gacchati, na manomayo attapaṭilābhoti saṅkhaṃ "
"gacchati;"
msgstr ""
"While in a non-physical reincarnation, it’s not referred to as a substantial "
"or mind-made reincarnation,"

msgctxt "dn9:83.6"
msgid "arūpo attapaṭilābhotveva tasmiṃ samaye saṅkhaṃ gacchati."
msgstr "only as a non-physical reincarnation."

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="75"></a>
msgctxt "dn9:84.1"
msgid "Sace taṃ, citta, evaṃ puccheyyuṃ:"
msgstr "Citta, suppose they were to ask you:"

msgctxt "dn9:84.2"
msgid "‘ahosi tvaṃ atītamaddhānaṃ, na tvaṃ nāhosi;"
msgstr "‘Did you exist in the past?"

msgctxt "dn9:84.3"
msgid "bhavissasi tvaṃ anāgatamaddhānaṃ, na tvaṃ na bhavissasi;"
msgstr "Will you exist in the future?"

msgctxt "dn9:84.4"
msgid "atthi tvaṃ etarahi, na tvaṃ natthī’ti."
msgstr "Do you exist now?’"

msgctxt "dn9:84.5"
msgid "Evaṃ puṭṭho tvaṃ, citta, kinti byākareyyāsī”ti?"
msgstr "How would you answer?”"

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="76"></a>
msgctxt "dn9:85.1"
msgid "“Sace maṃ, bhante, evaṃ puccheyyuṃ:"
msgstr "“Sir, if they were to ask me this,"

msgctxt "dn9:85.2"
msgid "‘ahosi tvaṃ atītamaddhānaṃ, na tvaṃ na ahosi;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn9:85.3"
msgid "bhavissasi tvaṃ anāgatamaddhānaṃ, na tvaṃ na bhavissasi;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn9:85.4"
msgid "atthi tvaṃ etarahi, na tvaṃ natthī’ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn9:85.5"
msgid "Evaṃ puṭṭho ahaṃ, bhante, evaṃ byākareyyaṃ:"
msgstr "I’d answer like this: "

msgctxt "dn9:85.6"
msgid "‘ahosāhaṃ atītamaddhānaṃ, nāhaṃ na ahosiṃ;"
msgstr "‘I existed in the past."

msgctxt "dn9:85.7"
msgid "bhavissāmahaṃ anāgatamaddhānaṃ, nāhaṃ na bhavissāmi;"
msgstr "I will exist in the future."

msgctxt "dn9:85.8"
msgid "atthāhaṃ etarahi, nāhaṃ natthī’ti."
msgstr "I exist now.’"

msgctxt "dn9:85.9"
msgid "Evaṃ puṭṭho ahaṃ, bhante, evaṃ byākareyyan”ti."
msgstr "That’s how I’d answer.”"

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="77"></a><a class="wp" id="wp50"></a>
msgctxt "dn9:86.1"
msgid "“Sace pana taṃ, citta, evaṃ puccheyyuṃ:"
msgstr "“But Citta, suppose they were to ask you: "

#. VAR: sova → svera (bj, pts1) | soyeva (s1-3) | so ca (mr)
msgctxt "dn9:86.2"
msgid ""
"‘yo te ahosi atīto attapaṭilābho, sova te attapaṭilābho sacco, mogho "
"anāgato, mogho paccuppanno?"
msgstr ""
"‘Is the reincarnation you had in the past your only real one, and those of "
"the future and present fictitious?"

#. VAR: Yo → yo va (pts1)
msgctxt "dn9:86.3"
msgid ""
"Yo te bhavissati anāgato attapaṭilābho, sova te attapaṭilābho sacco, mogho "
"atīto, mogho paccuppanno?"
msgstr ""
"Is the reincarnation you will have in the future your only real one, and "
"those of the past and present fictitious?"

msgctxt "dn9:86.4"
msgid ""
"Yo te etarahi paccuppanno attapaṭilābho, sova te attapaṭilābho sacco, mogho "
"atīto, mogho anāgato’ti."
msgstr ""
"Is the reincarnation you have now your only real one, and those of the past "
"and future fictitious?’"

msgctxt "dn9:86.5"
msgid "Evaṃ puṭṭho tvaṃ, citta, kinti byākareyyāsī”ti?"
msgstr "How would you answer?”"

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="78"></a><a class="pts" id="pts1.201"></a>
msgctxt "dn9:87.1"
msgid "“Sace pana maṃ, bhante, evaṃ puccheyyuṃ:"
msgstr "“Sir, if they were to ask me this,"

msgctxt "dn9:87.2"
msgid ""
"‘yo te ahosi atīto attapaṭilābho, sova te attapaṭilābho sacco, mogho "
"anāgato, mogho paccuppanno."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn9:87.3"
msgid ""
"Yo te bhavissati anāgato attapaṭilābho, sova te attapaṭilābho sacco, mogho "
"atīto, mogho paccuppanno."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn9:87.4"
msgid ""
"Yo te etarahi paccuppanno attapaṭilābho, sova te attapaṭilābho sacco, mogho "
"atīto, mogho anāgato’ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn9:87.5"
msgid "Evaṃ puṭṭho ahaṃ, bhante, evaṃ byākareyyaṃ:"
msgstr "I’d answer like this: "

msgctxt "dn9:87.6"
msgid ""
"‘yo me ahosi atīto attapaṭilābho, sova me attapaṭilābho tasmiṃ samaye sacco "
"ahosi, mogho anāgato, mogho paccuppanno."
msgstr ""
"‘The reincarnation I had in the past was real at that time, and those of the "
"future and present fictitious."

msgctxt "dn9:87.7"
msgid ""
"Yo me bhavissati anāgato attapaṭilābho, sova me attapaṭilābho tasmiṃ samaye "
"sacco bhavissati, mogho atīto, mogho paccuppanno."
msgstr ""
"The reincarnation I will have in the future will be real at the time, and "
"those of the past and present fictitious."

msgctxt "dn9:87.8"
msgid ""
"Yo me etarahi paccuppanno attapaṭilābho, sova me attapaṭilābho sacco, mogho "
"atīto, mogho anāgato’ti."
msgstr ""
"The reincarnation I have now is real at this time, and those of the past and "
"future fictitious.’"

msgctxt "dn9:87.9"
msgid "Evaṃ puṭṭho ahaṃ, bhante, evaṃ byākareyyan”ti."
msgstr "That’s how I’d answer.”"

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="79"></a><a class="wp" id="wp51"></a>
msgctxt "dn9:88.1"
msgid ""
"“Evameva kho, citta, yasmiṃ samaye oḷāriko attapaṭilābho hoti, neva tasmiṃ "
"samaye manomayo attapaṭilābhoti saṅkhaṃ gacchati, na arūpo attapaṭilābhoti "
"saṅkhaṃ gacchati."
msgstr ""
"“In the same way, while in any one of the three reincarnations, it’s not "
"referred to as the other two, only under its own name."

msgctxt "dn9:88.2"
msgid "Oḷāriko attapaṭilābhotveva tasmiṃ samaye saṅkhaṃ gacchati."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn9:88.3"
msgid "Yasmiṃ, citta, samaye manomayo attapaṭilābho hoti …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn9:88.4"
msgid "pe …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn9:88.5"
msgid ""
"yasmiṃ, citta, samaye arūpo attapaṭilābho hoti, neva tasmiṃ samaye oḷāriko "
"attapaṭilābhoti saṅkhaṃ gacchati, na manomayo attapaṭilābhoti saṅkhaṃ "
"gacchati;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn9:88.6"
msgid "arūpo attapaṭilābhotveva tasmiṃ samaye saṅkhaṃ gacchati."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="80"></a><a class="wp" id="wp52"></a><a class="pts"
#. id="pts1.202"></a>
msgctxt "dn9:89.1"
msgid ""
"Seyyathāpi, citta, gavā khīraṃ, khīramhā dadhi, dadhimhā navanītaṃ, "
"navanītamhā sappi, sappimhā sappimaṇḍo."
msgstr ""
"From a cow comes milk, from milk comes curds, from curds come butter, from "
"butter comes ghee, and from ghee comes cream of ghee. And the cream of ghee "
"is said to be the best of these.  "

msgctxt "dn9:89.2"
msgid ""
"Yasmiṃ samaye khīraṃ hoti, neva tasmiṃ samaye dadhīti saṅkhaṃ gacchati, na "
"navanītanti saṅkhaṃ gacchati, na sappīti saṅkhaṃ gacchati, na sappimaṇḍoti "
"saṅkhaṃ gacchati;"
msgstr ""
"While it’s milk, it’s not referred to as curds, butter, ghee, or cream of "
"ghee."

msgctxt "dn9:89.3"
msgid "khīrantveva tasmiṃ samaye saṅkhaṃ gacchati."
msgstr "It’s only referred to as milk."

msgctxt "dn9:89.4"
msgid "Yasmiṃ samaye dadhi hoti …"
msgstr "While it’s curd"

msgctxt "dn9:89.5"
msgid "pe …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn9:89.6"
msgid "navanītaṃ hoti …"
msgstr "or butter"

msgctxt "dn9:89.7"
msgid "sappi hoti …"
msgstr "or ghee"

msgctxt "dn9:89.8"
msgid ""
"sappimaṇḍo hoti, neva tasmiṃ samaye khīranti saṅkhaṃ gacchati, na dadhīti "
"saṅkhaṃ gacchati, na navanītanti saṅkhaṃ gacchati, na sappīti saṅkhaṃ "
"gacchati;"
msgstr "or cream of ghee, it’s not referred to as anything else,"

msgctxt "dn9:89.9"
msgid "sappimaṇḍotveva tasmiṃ samaye saṅkhaṃ gacchati."
msgstr "only under its own name."

#. <a class="wp" id="wp53"></a>
msgctxt "dn9:89.10"
msgid "Evameva kho, citta, yasmiṃ samaye oḷāriko attapaṭilābho hoti …"
msgstr ""
"In the same way, while in any one of the three reincarnations, it’s not "
"referred to as the other two, only under its own name."

msgctxt "dn9:89.11"
msgid "pe …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn9:89.12"
msgid "yasmiṃ, citta, samaye manomayo attapaṭilābho hoti …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn9:89.13"
msgid "pe …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn9:89.14"
msgid ""
"yasmiṃ, citta, samaye arūpo attapaṭilābho hoti, neva tasmiṃ samaye oḷāriko "
"attapaṭilābhoti saṅkhaṃ gacchati, na manomayo attapaṭilābhoti saṅkhaṃ "
"gacchati;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn9:89.15"
msgid "arūpo attapaṭilābhotveva tasmiṃ samaye saṅkhaṃ gacchati."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn9:89.16"
msgid ""
"Imā kho, citta, lokasamaññā lokaniruttiyo lokavohārā lokapaññattiyo, yāhi "
"tathāgato voharati aparāmasan”ti."
msgstr ""
"These are the world’s usages, terms, expressions, and descriptions, which "
"the Realized One uses without misapprehending them.”"

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="81"></a><a class="wp" id="wp54"></a>
msgctxt "dn9:90.1"
msgid "Evaṃ vutte, poṭṭhapādo paribbājako bhagavantaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr "When he said this, the wanderer Poṭṭhapāda said to the Buddha:"

msgctxt "dn9:90.2"
msgid "“abhikkantaṃ, bhante, abhikkantaṃ, bhante."
msgstr "“Excellent, sir! Excellent!"

msgctxt "dn9:90.3"
msgid ""
"Seyyathāpi, bhante, nikkujjitaṃ vā ukkujjeyya, paṭicchannaṃ vā vivareyya, "
"mūḷhassa vā maggaṃ ācikkheyya, andhakāre vā telapajjotaṃ dhāreyya:"
msgstr ""
"As if he was righting the overturned, or revealing the hidden, or pointing "
"out the path to the lost, or lighting a lamp in the dark  "

msgctxt "dn9:90.4"
msgid "‘cakkhumanto rūpāni dakkhantī’ti;"
msgstr "so people with good eyes can see what’s there,  "

msgctxt "dn9:90.5"
msgid "evamevaṃ bhagavatā anekapariyāyena dhammo pakāsito."
msgstr "so too the Buddha has made the teaching clear in many ways. "

msgctxt "dn9:90.6"
msgid ""
"Esāhaṃ, bhante, bhagavantaṃ saraṇaṃ gacchāmi dhammañca bhikkhusaṅghañca."
msgstr ""
"I go for refuge to the Buddha, to the Dharma, and to the mendicant Saṅgha."

msgctxt "dn9:90.7"
msgid "Upāsakaṃ maṃ bhagavā dhāretu ajjatagge pāṇupetaṃ saraṇaṃ gatan”ti."
msgstr ""
"From this day forth, may the Buddha remember me as a lay follower who has "
"gone for refuge for life.” "

#. </p><h3>
msgctxt "dn9:91.1"
msgid "2.3. Cittahatthisāriputtaupasampadā"
msgstr "The Ordination of Citta Hatthisāriputta"

#. </h3><p><a class="sc" id="82"></a><a class="wp" id="wp55"></a>
msgctxt "dn9:92.1"
msgid "Citto pana hatthisāriputto bhagavantaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr "But Citta Hatthisāriputta said to the Buddha:"

msgctxt "dn9:92.2"
msgid "“abhikkantaṃ, bhante, abhikkantaṃ, bhante."
msgstr "“Excellent, sir! Excellent!"

msgctxt "dn9:92.3"
msgid ""
"Seyyathāpi, bhante, nikkujjitaṃ vā ukkujjeyya, paṭicchannaṃ vā vivareyya, "
"mūḷhassa vā maggaṃ ācikkheyya, andhakāre vā telapajjotaṃ dhāreyya:"
msgstr ""
"As if he was righting the overturned, or revealing the hidden, or pointing "
"out the path to the lost, or lighting a lamp in the dark  "

msgctxt "dn9:92.4"
msgid "‘cakkhumanto rūpāni dakkhantī’ti;"
msgstr "so people with good eyes can see what’s there,  "

msgctxt "dn9:92.5"
msgid "evamevaṃ bhagavatā anekapariyāyena dhammo pakāsito."
msgstr "so too the Buddha has made the teaching clear in many ways. "

msgctxt "dn9:92.6"
msgid ""
"Esāhaṃ, bhante, bhagavantaṃ saraṇaṃ gacchāmi dhammañca bhikkhusaṅghañca."
msgstr ""
"I go for refuge to the Buddha, to the Dharma, and to the mendicant Saṅgha."

msgctxt "dn9:92.7"
msgid ""
"Labheyyāhaṃ, bhante, bhagavato santike pabbajjaṃ, labheyyaṃ upasampadan”ti."
msgstr ""
"Sir, may I receive the going forth, the ordination in the Buddha’s presence?”"
" "

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="83"></a><a class="wp" id="wp56"></a><a class="pts"
#. id="pts1.203"></a>
msgctxt "dn9:93.1"
msgid ""
"Alattha kho citto hatthisāriputto bhagavato santike pabbajjaṃ, alattha "
"upasampadaṃ."
msgstr ""
"And Citta Hatthisāriputta received the going forth, the ordination in the "
"Buddha’s presence."

msgctxt "dn9:93.2"
msgid ""
"Acirūpasampanno kho panāyasmā citto hatthisāriputto eko vūpakaṭṭho appamatto "
"ātāpī pahitatto viharanto na cirasseva—"
msgstr ""
"Not long after his ordination, Venerable Citta Hatthisāriputta, living "
"alone, withdrawn, diligent, keen, and determined, soon "

msgctxt "dn9:93.3"
msgid ""
"yassatthāya kulaputtā sammadeva agārasmā anagāriyaṃ pabbajanti, tadanuttaraṃ—"
msgstr ""
"realized the supreme end of the spiritual path in this very life. He lived "
"having achieved with his own insight the goal for which people from good "
"families rightly go forth from the lay life to homelessness.   "

msgctxt "dn9:93.4"
msgid ""
"brahmacariyapariyosānaṃ diṭṭheva dhamme sayaṃ abhiññā sacchikatvā "
"upasampajja vihāsi."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn9:93.5"
msgid ""
"“Khīṇā jāti, vusitaṃ brahmacariyaṃ, kataṃ karaṇīyaṃ, nāparaṃ itthattāyā”ti—"
msgstr ""
"He understood: “Rebirth is ended; the spiritual life has been lived; what "
"had to be done has been done; there is no return to any state of existence.” "

msgctxt "dn9:93.6"
msgid "abbhaññāsi."
msgstr ""

# Not without some wavering, according to AN 6.60
msgctxt "dn9:93.7"
msgid "Aññataro kho panāyasmā citto hatthisāriputto arahataṃ ahosīti."
msgstr "And Venerable Citta Hatthisāriputta became one of the perfected."

#. </p><p class="endsutta">
msgctxt "dn9:94.1"
msgid "Poṭṭhapādasuttaṃ niṭṭhitaṃ navamaṃ."
msgstr ""
